      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, you have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one! It drives like a dream and looks virtually brand new, inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been cared for with a lot of love and looks like it just rolled off the lot, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
