      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system in peak operational order. The drivetrain remains tight, utilizing a Getrag 6-speed manual to channel power through a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally pristine, with a fully documented subframe inspection and zero evidence of fatigue. Every bushing, damper, and suspension link remains within factory tolerances, offering the precise, communicative handling that defines the marque. This is a concours-level specimen with a flawless service history, free of the common rod bearing or VANOS issues associated with higher-mileage units.",
